  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/f039ba4d14331ac6a0a3d1739fefcb9c.poster.avif?t=1739200120\" width=320 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/f039ba4d14331ac6a0a3d1739fefcb9c.webm?t=1739200120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/f039ba4d14331ac6a0a3d1739fefcb9c.mp4?t=1739200120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quarrel Hill is an action clicker game with upgrades. You need to destroy or push your enemies off a cliff before they do the same to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/fb874d2af1ac1ec8b33e1a710ef9f0d2.apng?t=1739200120\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/fb874d2af1ac1ec8b33e1a710ef9f0d2.poster.avif?t=1739200120\" class=\"bb_img\" width=182 height=176 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/a6671cefb27d48640bb5375f9f1ae5b7.apng?t=1739200120\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/a6671cefb27d48640bb5375f9f1ae5b7.poster.avif?t=1739200120\" class=\"bb_img\" width=280 height=182 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/4bc7fb984b1dfd48d6e8fa06d90126aa.apng?t=1739200120\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/4bc7fb984b1dfd48d6e8fa06d90126aa.poster.avif?t=1739200120\" class=\"bb_img\" width=60 height=91 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spam click to push, rest to slash</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade and combine your team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >500 Levels teaming with enemies such as slimes, goblins, orcs, lizards, scorpions etc. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21 heroes with different special attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 biomes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player vs player</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/3eaf96d11bcfefe61824fdbd420f3ae8.poster.avif?t=1739200120\" width=662 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/3eaf96d11bcfefe61824fdbd420f3ae8.webm?t=1739200120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/3eaf96d11bcfefe61824fdbd420f3ae8.mp4?t=1739200120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each hero has got a unique special ability such as sneeze, freeze, poison, earthquake etc. You can combine  different special attacks at the same time selecting various heroes to your team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/a0a0519fbc1962a3703270966461a0db.poster.avif?t=1739200120\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/a0a0519fbc1962a3703270966461a0db.webm?t=1739200120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/a0a0519fbc1962a3703270966461a0db.mp4?t=1739200120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade HP, strength, pushing force and special attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play single player campaign or against your friend in PvP hot seat mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/f816da7753c3107e5ff4c262d5dfb87e.poster.avif?t=1739200120\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/f816da7753c3107e5ff4c262d5dfb87e.webm?t=1739200120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914130/extras/f816da7753c3107e5ff4c262d5dfb87e.mp4?t=1739200120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
